This is a what the company Oneteam does: Oneteam is built for non-desk workers, who are not sitting behind a desk. It is often very difficult to reach and engage them properly in the organization, which is why Oneteam bundled several components together in 1 mobile application to provide employees with an accessible and approachable platform. This native app, which can be downloaded on Android and iOs, consists of the following features:

- Internal communication: Centralize all internal communication on your own private and feed;
- Onboarding: Get new employees productive and engaged faster;
- E-Learning: Keep training and updating employees on new skills, guidelines, or processes;
- Surveys: Collect valuable feedback from your employees, later this year we will add the feature pulse surveys;
- Forms: Improve operational efficiency with digital forms and checklists.

